SHOOTING SETTING

MULTIPLE EXPOSURE CTRL

OptionDescription
ADDITIVEThe camera adds the exposures together. You may need to lower exposure compensation depending on the number of shots.
AVERAGEThe camera automatically optimizes exposure for the final pic- ture. The background in series shot without changing the com- position will be optimally exposed.
BRIGHTThe camera compares the exposures and chooses only the brightest pixel at each location. Colors may be mixed depending on their brightness and hue.
DARKThe camera compares the exposures and chooses only the dark- est pixel at each location. Colors may be mixed depending on their brightness and hue.

The camera can combine up to nine exposures.

SHOOTING SETTING

# MULTIPLE EXPOSURE CTRL

Choose how the camera combines shots to create a multiple ex-
posure.

![image](/image/placeholder)
+ →

| Option | Description |
| --- | --- |
| ADDITIVE | The camera adds the exposures together. You may need to lower exposure compensation depending on the number of shots. |
| AVERAGE | The camera automatically optimizes exposure for the final pic- ture. The background in series shot without changing the com- position will be optimally exposed. |
| BRIGHT | The camera compares the exposures and chooses only the brightest pixel at each location. Colors may be mixed depending on their brightness and hue. |
| DARK | The camera compares the exposures and chooses only the dark- est pixel at each location. Colors may be mixed depending on their brightness and hue. |


The camera can combine up to nine exposures.
